#!ek9
<?-
  Literal Validation Fuzz Test: Float - Underflow to Zero
  Tests if EK9 catches float underflow (value rounds to zero) at compile time.

  Expected: Should fail or warn (e-400 exponent underflows to zero)
  Actual: Compiles successfully, becomes unset at runtime
-?>
defines module fuzz.literal.float.underflow
  defines program
    TestUnderflowZero()
      f <- 1e-400
      stdout <- Stdout()
      if f?
        stdout.println("Set")
//EOF
